/***************************************************************************\
/****ANDROID BLUETOOTH SMART SAMPLE APP FLOWER POWER LIVE NOTIFICATION  ****\
/*********         TO BBOX API NEW ROOM NOTIFICATION                      **\
/***************************************************************************\

_ Scan and filter all Flower power devices
_ connect to selected flower power devices
_ discover automatically all services related to this device
_ register to 5 characteristics notifications on the device : sun light / soil EC / soil WC / soil temperature / air temperature
_ send all these notifications on the fly to Bbox Api new room notification (named /Message/Bluetooth)



